com.github.fge.jsonschema.walk
Class SchemaWalker

java.lang.Object
  com.github.fge.jsonschema.walk.SchemaWalker
Direct Known Subclasses:
ResolvingSchemaWalker, SimpleSchemaWalker
public abstract class SchemaWalker
extends Object

Main schema walker class

This class walks a JSON Schema (in the shape of a SchemaTree recursively. In order to visit subschemas, it relies on a series of PointerCollector instances (provided by a dictionary) to get the knowledge of what schemas to visit next.

Only subschemas are visited: unknown keywords, or keywords not having any subschemas, are ignored.

Important: the initial schema must be syntactically valid.

See Also:
SimpleSchemaWalker, ResolvingSchemaWalker
